# KVM host information for this tutorial

CPU: 2X Intel Xeon X5670 @ 2.93GHz

RAM: 140G

STORAGE:
vm images mounted on /data/images
vm data disks mounted on /data/disks

NETWORKS:
2x 1G cards in 802.3ad bond
3 routable VLAN interaces
 - VLAN 1: management nework
 - VLAN 2: tenant network
 - vlan 3: provider network
3 bridges for VM use
 - br0: management
 - br2: tenant
 - br4: provider
1 internal bridge
 - br-svc
